Solar System 3D Simulator with Advanced Apsidal Mechanics
Author: Emmanuel Forgues <solarsystem@forgues.eu>
Version: 1.0.0
Date: August 19, 2025

This project implements a scientifically accurate 3D solar system simulator
using real astronomical data from NASA/JPL and advanced orbital mechanics
calculations including Kepler's equation solving and apsidal precession.
